abstract: There’s no “impartial justice,” just protection of Trump at all costs.
snippet: There’s no “impartial justice,” just protection of Trump at all costs.
lead_paragraph: The impeachment trial of Donald John Trump began on Thursday when John Roberts, the chief justice of the Supreme Court, directed all of the senators to stand and raise their right hands. Ever since I can’t get two questions out of my head.

abstract: Senators Bernie Sanders and Elizabeth Warren argue over what was said at a private 2018 meeting, their dispute takes center stage at the debate and Cory Booker says goodbye.
snippet: Senators Bernie Sanders and Elizabeth Warren argue over what was said at a private 2018 meeting, their dispute takes center stage at the debate and Cory Booker says goodbye.
lead_paragraph: With less than three weeks to go before the Iowa caucuses, tensions escalated between two of the leading Democratic candidates and were on display on national television at a debate in Iowa.

abstract: Texts raised more questions about information suggesting that the United States ambassador to Ukraine was under surveillance.
snippet: Texts raised more questions about information suggesting that the United States ambassador to Ukraine was under surveillance.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — House Democrats released another round of information on Friday that raised questions about elements of the impeachment inquiry, including allegations about the surveillance of the United States ambassador in Ukraine and efforts by an aide to a top congressional Republican to pursue investigations sought by President Trump.

abstract: President Trump claims Nancy Pelosi has intentionally undermined Bernie Sanders’s presidential campaign by delaying the impeachment trial. Mr. Sanders denounced that theory on Friday.
snippet: President Trump claims Nancy Pelosi has intentionally undermined Bernie Sanders’s presidential campaign by delaying the impeachment trial. Mr. Sanders denounced that theory on Friday.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The first version of the conspiracy theory was hatched on Twitter last Friday, Jan. 10.

abstract: Lev Parnas has shown us Trumpism from the inside.
snippet: Lev Parnas has shown us Trumpism from the inside.
lead_paragraph: One good thing about surrounding yourself with tawdry gangsters and grifters is that if they flip on you, you can claim they have no credibility because they’re criminals.

headline_main: When Trump’s Thugs Turn on Him

abstract: In the Trump era, some voters say the power of a symbolic first is overshadowed by anxiety about defeating him.
snippet: In the Trump era, some voters say the power of a symbolic first is overshadowed by anxiety about defeating him.
lead_paragraph: WINTERSET, Iowa — Almost exactly three years ago, Leila Schlenker marveled at the crowds at the Women’s March in Des Moines, which drew more than 26,000 people to the grounds of the state capitol and reminded her of the large social protests of the 1960s.

abstract: Thousands of readers told us who they think should lead the Democratic Party — and the country.
snippet: Thousands of readers told us who they think should lead the Democratic Party — and the country.
lead_paragraph: On Sunday, The New York Times’s editorial board will announce which Democratic candidate it’s endorsing in the 2020 presidential race. This year, the board experimented with a new level of openness — publishing transcripts of the interviews with each of the candidates that led to its decision.
